{
  "stem": "10119.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 47.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they met a very ill fate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the Russians came in, and they raped their daughters, which the mothers had to stay and watch it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it wasn't such a beautiful-- beautiful sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I met those people in Kaschau after the war, which-- they were kind of sick.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there were-- it wasn't a bad process.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm trying to make it light, not as gory as it really was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm trying to modify it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it wasn't modified.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't nice at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was treachery from morning till night, suffering.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we tried to make the best of it, just hoping that tomorrow, the war will end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we will come out and find our families and start all over again, which is tough, still is.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Prague.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I remember, there were soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were speaking Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who they were, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they were [INAUDIBLE], or there was something who took care of the people who were transferring them after the war, I really don't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I know we were in trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came back to Prague.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were in a camp-- also and they put us in a camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From there, everybody-- we could do whatever we wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No papers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So from there, we looked around who was there, who was going where.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I decided, being that I was with a group from Kaschau, to go back to Kaschau.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did allow us to travel on the trains without any money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were taking us wherever we had to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever country we were in, they let us go free.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just got a group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to the train station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took us where we wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, once I came to Kaschau, there was also-- we got together in one big place, all of us, we-- we met.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From there, there was-- I don't know how you would call it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- I think the owner might have already worked with them because there were places which we were able to go in and to see what's what.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were able to get some food and sleep over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just like a transit place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From there, some of my friends did go to Sweden, six girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And being that I have found somebody who was going home-- so I decided that I'm not going to Sweden with you, which I wish I would have.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they went a complete-- they were there for six weeks with-- with psychologists, which helped them out a little bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went home to look for my family, which, with the train, there was also-- we always got a free ticket.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes you have to travel on the roof or sit on the floor, but we were always able to travel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're going to change tapes, and you tell me about what happened when you got back home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
